{"tid":2195853,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"沈振盈：港股仍有力上試二萬八關","createTime":"2020-09-09T12:11:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T05:58:53.000Z","uid":66271,"like":7,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"d2902882b9ec23bf2d8795e2f51f7c71013546e5","tid":2195853,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T12:11:49.000Z","msg":"踏入9月份首周，港股走勢偏軟，上周初美股大升，恒指卻未能作出突破。到了周四及周五，更出現較顯著的回落。雖則如是，恒指走勢仍是維持在8月的波幅區間之內。第3季全球股市大升，主要是利用央行放水托市，再配合炒疫情受控，經濟復甦的憧憬。<br />\n<br />\n然而，港股橫行上落了兩個多月，9月份季結，估計資金會乘機抽高來埋單。技術走勢上，較重要的阻力位分別在25,300點及25,800點，若能突破，後市應該會出現單邊升市<br />\n<br />\n從玄學的角度分析，星期一為「白露」，踏入「乙酉」月，對股市較上月有利。雖然美股上周出現跌勢，但港股表現相對穩定，相信9月份恒指仍望做好，有望挑戰28,000水平。"},{"pid":"3c9c1eaa474835f0af6323ba577e575b0d53772b","tid":2195853,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T12:19:42.000Z","msg":"9.81<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77aa0e2900e27ff02ad8e60216930d7d0c7222b8","tid":2195853,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T13:25:47.000Z","msg":"仆街了"},{"pid":"a7f280576791c1f3165ea177c26f73dda4a25cc7","tid":2195853,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T13:34:25.000Z","msg":"萬8見"},{"pid":"024d70c4240bf5f5d8affda5218b3e9e559c6be7","tid":2195853,"uid":249094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T15:08:41.000Z","msg":"屌你靜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b9727974c6d3679c790d6453193418da8d566c5","tid":2195853,"uid":97518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T09:04:55.000Z","msg":"一講完今日落番243"},{"pid":"4612528f2d584827f5b2c904a8ccf352134e1785","tid":2195853,"uid":173666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T09:06:42